  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1597311358571-I03WWB4PHHY9CPXSU7F5/8a-Amy%2BTangerine%2Bhand-scripted%2Bquote.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Know those people who just radiate goodness? Surround yourself with those kind of people.</p><p>Still trying to spread more love and motivation for each of your Mondays this year. I'm still using this watercolor set from Michaels and I got a new brush from a local art supply store, and found the Princeton Select brush online here at Joann. I'm using a new notebook from <a href=\"http://www.bookjournals.com\">Ex Libris Anonymous</a>. If you have a favorite quote – silly, snarky or simple in its’ wisdom, please share in the comments!</p><p>In case you missed it, I have some of my favorite quotes scanned in and available as printable PDF's <a href=\"/digishop\">in the shop</a>! Thanks as always for being an amazing blog reader!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
